<view class="result-page">
  <view class="section-card result-card">
    <text class="result-tag">ORDER CREATED</text>
    <text class="result-title">订单已提交</text>
    <text class="result-desc">当前版本已完成下单请求，下一步我们会继续接支付和订单详情。</text>
    <text class="result-desc" wx:if="{{roomDeliveryNotice}}">{{roomDeliveryNotice}}</text>
    <view class="result-info">
      <text>订单号：{{orderNo}}</text>
      <text>场景：{{orderSceneLabel}}</text>
      <text>金额：¥{{payableAmount}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="result-tips">
      <text class="result-desc">建议下一步：</text>
      <text class="result-desc" wx:if="{{orderScene === 'ROOM_DELIVERY'}}">1. 保持当前房间识别状态，后续仍可继续添加客房送餐订单。</text>
      <text class="result-desc" wx:else>1. 可继续浏览菜单补充点餐，也可以先去查看订单状态。</text>
      <text class="result-desc">2. 如需协助，可直接联系商家或前往服务中心查看其他服务。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="result-actions">
      <button bindtap="goOrders">查看我的订单</button>
      <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="backToMenu">继续点餐</button>
    </view>
    <view class="result-actions">
      <button bindtap="goServiceCenter">进入服务中心</button>
      <button wx:if="{{orderScene === 'ROOM_DELIVERY'}}" bindtap="goRoomDining">房间送餐设置</button>
    </view>
    <button class="ghost-btn contact-btn" wx:if="{{contactPhone}}" bindtap="callMerchant">联系商家</button>
  </view>
</view>
